text: Collecting the Dragon Breastplate, Dragon Pendant, Dragon Mask, and Dragon Spear reveals the power of the Dragon.
Collecting the Boots of Dreaming, Cloak of Dreaming, Ring of Dreaming, and Bow of Dreaming reveals the power of Dreams.
Collecting the Eagle Bracers, Eagle Quiver, Eagle Mask, and Eagle Bow reveals the power of the Eagle.
Collecting the Twilight Helm, Twilight Banner, Twilight Horn, and Twilight Spear reveals the power of Twilight.
